  "title": "Service Crew (Live Show – Bugis)",
  "description": "<p>📍 <strong>Bugis+</strong><br />💰 <strong>Salary:</strong> $2,100 – $2,400 (incl. night allowance up to $200/month)<br />🕒 <strong>Working Hours:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Night Shift: <strong>8:30pm – 3:30am</strong></p></li><li><p>44 hours/week</p></li><li><p><em>Minimum 4 hours OT/week required</em></p></li></ul><h2><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Assist with live show operations: serving, clearing, customer support</p></li><li><p>Manage crowd flow, seating, and order delivery</p></li><li><p>Maintain hygiene & service standards</p></li><li><p>Support performers and show crew where needed</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Service-oriented, lively & energetic</p></li><li><p>Comfortable in nightlife environment</p></li><li><p>Fast learner with positive attitude</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Benefits</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Referral Bonus</p></li><li><p>Medical & Dental Benefits</p></li><li><p>Company Transport</p></li><li><p>Birthday Ang Pao</p></li><li><p>Incremental Annual Leave (from 10 days)</p></li><li><p>Career Development<br /></p><p>EA License No: 23C1703</p><p>EA Personnel No: R1762582</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p></li></ul>",
